data.name: Family Vault Purple
data.description:
Bred in the mid 90s and shared between a small group of master growers in Mendocino's Long-Valley Region, her size and vigor is legendary. Despite a heavy indica parentage, her thick purple flowers are offset by an unexpected soaring sativa high when smoked. An early finisher, she emanates heavy overtones of crushed grapes, lavender essences, and toasted marshmallows bound over a vivid core of orchard blossoms, fresh earth, and cloves. 

Genetics: Spyrock Blueberry x Garberville Purple Kush

Flowering Time: 55-60 days indoor, Late September-Early October outdoors

Seeds per box: 10. Only 500 boxes released.

data.name: In The Pines
data.description:
Made famous by award-winning master grower Derek Emerald of Boonville, CA. She expresses razor sharp overtones of pineapple extract and citric acid. Aromas of rotten fruit are b found over a vivid core of crushed pine needles, orchard blossoms and lemon scented disinfectant. 

Genetics: Heirloom Pineapple Thai x Master Kush x Mean Gene's Pineapple

Flowering Time: 60-65 days indoors, Early-Mid October outdoors

Seeds per box: 10. Only 500 boxes released.

data.name: Royal Salute
data.description:
The Long-Valley Secret Sauce is rumored to be one of the earliest fuel strains in existence and for over a decade was shared strictly between a small group of elite growers in Mendocino. Gasoline infused lemon grass and cherry tart unwinding into an encore of citrus perfume, napalm, and chloroform. 

Genetics: 2013 Royal Sour x Long-Valley Secret Sauce

Flowering Time: 65-70 days indoors, Mid-Late October outdoors

Seeds per box: 10. Only 350 boxes released.

data.name: Red Hindu Kush
data.description:
For those in search of a pure heirloom indica, The Red Hindu is a highly robust large framed plant that exudes piercing overtones sliced guava and passion fruit glued together by a tight bouquet of grapefruit, lavender, and fresh forest soil.  Expect medium-large flower draped in oil and sugar. 

Genetics: Pure Kush x Leggett Hindu Kush x Big Red Hindu Kush

Flowering Time: 65-70 days indoors, Early-Mid October outdoors

Seeds per box: 10. Only 300 boxes released.
